<p><strong>Skills</strong> Medicine +4, Nature +4, Perception +4, Survival +6</p>

<p><strong>Languages</strong> Bothii, Common</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 2 (450 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Innate Spellcasting.</em></strong> The shaman can innately cast the following spells. Its spellcasting ability is Wisdom (spell save DC 12, +4 to hit with spell attacks).</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>At Will: dancing lights, message, mage hand, thaumaturgy</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>1/day: augury, bestow curse, cordon of arrows, detect magic, hex, prayer of healing, speak with dead, spirit guardians</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Spear.</em></strong> Melee or Ranged Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft. or range 20/60 ft., one target. Hit: 5 (1d6+2) piercing damage, or 6 (1d8 + 2) piercing damage if wielded with two hands.</p>

<p><strong><em>Shortbow.</em></strong> Ranged Weapon Attack: +3 to hit, range 80/320 ft., one target. Hit: 4 (1d6 + 1) piercing damage.</p>

